&lt;p&gt;For my use case was needed to change previous element style on focus and hover only having 2 items in parent  element. to do so used &lt;code&gt;:focus-within&lt;/code&gt; and &lt;code&gt;:hover&lt;/code&gt; pseudo-classes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;like so selecting whenever focus/hover event occurs&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;snippet&quot; data-lang=&quot;js&quot; data-hide=&quot;false&quot; data-console=&quot;true&quot; data-babel=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
